aces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n脾氣好真係一個好難得既優點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1aea93a32dfa799b4b552e8ce7a93b17699949","tid":150002,"uid":40993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:04:46.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近識咗個人 想同佢fd啲close啲 相處係好開心 但我成日覺得同佢無話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3502c02d5f124a587171fa2e9972561c6ccef518","tid":150002,"uid":88861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:42:31.000Z","msg":"價值觀 唔似已經玩完"},{"pid":"7b282265f5c6b243c0892835309fdcbf4619629b","tid":150002,"uid":31126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最近識咗個人 想同佢fd啲close啲 相處係好開心 但我成日覺得同佢無話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n情況完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果dead air可能會被扣分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff2b0ef506a10e4cb3a6a8b2d101f969dba6ebe","tid":150002,"uid":31126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>價值觀 唔似已經玩完</blockquote><br />\n唯有盡可能搵個大家都比較接受既角度去睇事物 搵個平衡點<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a0228bd9bae88dac986e71aec8770aed1c3b98","tid":150002,"uid":85989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"性格唔同唔緊要 一凹一凸先好<br />\n但最緊要價值觀唔可以差太遠"},{"pid":"1fcf2664a361c92b1013402f439feb5ef4e1874a","tid":150002,"uid":85253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0